Here’s a TekAutomate Steps UI flow to measure rise time, fall time, peak-to-peak, and mean on CH2 for an MSO4/5/6 Series oscilloscope. Each measurement is set up using the write step with the appropriate SCPI command.

```json
{
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Rise Time Measurement on CH2",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS1:SOURCE CH2"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Rise Time Type for MEAS1",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS1:TYPE RIS"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Fall Time Measurement on CH2",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS2:SOURCE CH2"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Fall Time Type for MEAS2",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS2:TYPE FALL"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Peak-to-Peak Measurement on CH2",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS3:SOURCE CH2"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Peak-to-Peak Type for MEAS3",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS3:TYPE PK2PK"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Mean Measurement on CH2",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS4:SOURCE CH2"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "write",
      "label": "Set Mean Type for MEAS4",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS4:TYPE MEAN"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

This flow configures four measurements (rise time, fall time, pk2pk, mean) on channel 2. If you want to read out the results, add query steps for each measurement value:

```json
{
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "query",
      "label": "Query Rise Time (MEAS1)",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS1:VALUE?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "label": "Query Fall Time (MEAS2)",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS2:VALUE?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "label": "Query Peak-to-Peak (MEAS3)",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS3:VALUE?"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "query",
      "label": "Query Mean (MEAS4)",
      "params": {
        "command": "MEASUREMENT:MEAS4:VALUE?"
      }
    }
  ]
}
```

Let me know if you want the query steps included in the main flow!

